# gemma4:e4b - best config (Google Gemma 4 E4B, thinking-capable, run non-thinking)
# Gemma 4 E4B: 8B total weights, ~4.5B effective (MatFormer), Q4_K_M, 128K native context.
# temp 1.0 / top_k 64 / top_p 0.95 = Google/Unsloth recommended sampling (HF: high temp best
# for coding). E4B thinking is OFF by default (enable via <|think|> in system prompt).
# Measured: temp 1.0 and an earlier (wrong) 0.7 give identical benchmark scores here.
# ollama create gemma-best -f configs/gemma.best.Modelfile
FROM gemma4:e4b
PARAMETER temperature 1.0
PARAMETER top_k 64
PARAMETER top_p 0.95
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
